---
description: agentic-setup project conventions for TypeScript CLI development
alwaysApply: true
---
- Relative imports must end with `.js` extensions.
- Use `unknown` instead of `any` for type safety.
- Run tests: `npm run test` or `npx vitest run tests/scoring/accuracy.test.ts`.
- Conventional commits format: `feat:`, `fix:`, `refactor:`.